casebody.data:
Randi BLUMENTHAL-GUIGUI, etc., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Marc GIDNEY, etc., et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1657 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 15, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SUAREZ and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, and the responses and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied without prejudice to seek a stay from the trial court of the trial court's order submitting the parties to mediation until resolution of the petitioner's motion to dismiss for lack of subject matter jurisdiction.
